Package gui.sub

Class Summary
AddToWaitlistUI This class is pop up dialog box that is used to add patients to the waitlist.
ChangePriorityUI Dialog popup that allows the date entered set for a waitlist entry to be changed in order to alter the priorities.
DefaultTimeslotsUI This is the Dialog pop that can be accessed from the the administrator menu.
DisplayAppointmentConfirmationUI DisplayAppointmentConfirmationUI shows information about a patient's appointment when a patient in the table is clicked.
DisplayAppointmentSearchUI DisplayAppointmentSearchUI shows information about an appointment when an appointment in the table is clicked.
DisplayPatientSearchUI DisplayPatientSearchUI shows information about a patient when a patient in the search table is clicked.
DisplayPractitionerUI Displays the info on a practitioner when a scheduled one is double clicked.
DisplayWaitingPatientUI Displays information on an entry in the waitlist.
EditAppointmentUI  
EditPatientsUI Displays a list of all of the patients and allows a patient to be selected for editing or removal Also allows creation of new patients.
EditPatientUI Pop-up dialog for the editing of a single patient.
EditPractitionersUI Displays a list practitioners and allows one to be selected for editing or deletion.
EditPractitionerUI Popup that allows a single practitioner's details to be edited
HelpUI Popup that displays the full manual for the application.
NewPatientUI Popup that allows new patients to be created
NewPractitionerUI Popup that allows new practitioners to be created.
NewTypeUI Tiny popup that allows new types to be created.
SearchForAppointmentUI Displays the pop up window that allows the user to search for the next available appointment.
SearchForPatientUI Displays the pop up window that allows the user to search for a patient.
SelectPatientUI Popup that appears when an empty appointment block is double clicked or when the button is clicked.
SelectPractitionerUI Popup that appears when the schedule practitioner button is clicked.
SelectTimeSlotUI Popup that allows the hours of operation in a day to be changed.
